 phase shift with a known R.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Use an external AC source to study the phase and amplitude at different
 frequencies
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Use L and C in series to observe resonance, zero phase shift when 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega L=\frac{1}{\omega C}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

